lead_paragraph: Just as the video celebrating his first 600 wins was wrapping up, Kansas coach Bill Self turned to his left and saw Frank Mason III, extending a ball to him to commemorate the milestone.

headline.print_headline: Kansas Rolls Over UMKC 105-62 to Give Bill Self Win No. 600
